---
import MarketingLayout from "../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "December 20, 2025";
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for FloImg and FloImg Studio"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">
          Welcome to FloImg, a product of Flojo, Inc. ("Company", "we", "our", "us"). These Terms of
          Service ("Terms") govern your use of FloImg, FloImg Studio, and related services
          (collectively, the "Service").
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">
          By accessing or using the Service, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you disagree
          with any part of these terms, you may not access the Service.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
          Please also review our <a
            href="/privacy"
            class="text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a
          >, which explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Cloud vs Self-Hosted -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          2. Cloud Service vs Self-Hosted
        </h2>

        <div
          class="bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-900/20 border border-teal-200 dark:border-teal-800 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-teal-900 dark:text-teal-200 mb-2">
            FloImg Cloud (studio.floimg.com)
          </h3>
          <p class="text-teal-800 dark:text-teal-300 mb-4">
            Our hosted cloud service has strict content policies. All content generated or uploaded
            is subject to automated moderation and human review. <strong
              >Absolutely no harmful, illegal, or inappropriate content is permitted.</strong
            >
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-teal-800 dark:text-teal-300 space-y-1">
            <li>All content is scanned before being saved</li>
            <li>Violations result in content removal and potential account suspension</li>
            <li>We maintain a zero-tolerance policy for illegal content</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 rounded-lg p-6"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
            Self-Hosted FloImg Studio
          </h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">
            The self-hosted version of FloImg Studio is provided under the MIT License. While you
            are free to use, modify, and distribute the software, you remain responsible for:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 space-y-1">
            <li>Content generated on your own infrastructure</li>
            <li>Compliance with applicable laws in your jurisdiction</li>
            <li>Implementing appropriate content moderation if needed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Prohibited Content -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          3. Prohibited Content
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">
          The following content is strictly prohibited on our cloud service and may not be created
          using floimg software for illegal purposes:
        </p>

        <div
          class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800 rounded-lg p-6"
        >
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">1.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-200"
                  >Child Sexual Abuse Material (CSAM)</strong
                >
                <p class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 text-sm">
                  This is a criminal offense. We report all instances to appropriate authorities.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">2.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-200"
                  >Pornographic or Sexually Explicit Content</strong
                >
                <p class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 text-sm">
                  Including AI-generated sexual imagery of any kind.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">3.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-200">Violent or Graphic Content</strong>
                <p class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 text-sm">
                  Gore, extreme violence, or content depicting harm to individuals.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">4.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-200"
                  >Hate Speech and Discrimination</strong
                >
                <p class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 text-sm">
                  Content that promotes hatred based on race, ethnicity, religion, gender, sexual
                  orientation, disability, or other protected characteristics.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">5.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-200">Harassment and Threats</strong>
                <p class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 text-sm">
                  Content intended to harass, threaten, or intimidate individuals.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">6.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-200">Copyright Infringement</strong>
                <p class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 text-sm">
                  Reproducing copyrighted material without permission.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">7.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-200">Malware and Harmful Links</strong>
                <p class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 text-sm">
                  QR codes or content linking to malicious websites or downloads.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">8.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-200">Spam and Abuse</strong>
                <p class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 text-sm">
                  Automated abuse of the service or promotional spam.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Content Moderation -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          4. Content Moderation
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">
          To maintain a safe environment, we employ the following moderation measures on our cloud
          service:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>
            <strong>Automated Scanning:</strong> All generated and uploaded content is scanned by AI moderation
            systems before being saved.
          </li>
          <li><strong>Human Review:</strong> Flagged content is reviewed by our team.</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Pre-moderation for Public Gallery:</strong> Content submitted to the public gallery
            requires approval before publication.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Incident Logging:</strong> Violations are logged for security and legal compliance
            purposes.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
          Content that violates our policies will be removed without notice. Repeat violators will
          have their accounts suspended or permanently banned.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- User Responsibilities -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          5. User Responsibilities
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">By using the Service, you agree to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 space-y-2">
          <li>Not create, upload, or share prohibited content</li>
          <li>Use the Service only for lawful purposes</li>
          <li>Not attempt to circumvent content moderation systems</li>
          <li>Report any violations you encounter</li>
          <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Open Source License -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          6. Open Source License
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">
          floimg and floimg Studio are open source software provided under the MIT License. This
          means you are free to use, modify, and distribute the software.
        </p>
        <div
          class="bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 rounded-lg p-6 font-mono text-sm"
        >
          <p class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
            This software is provided under the MIT License. While you are free to use, modify, and
            distribute this software, you may NOT use it to create, store, or distribute illegal
            content. The creators of this software are not responsible for how it is used by third
            parties.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Disclaimer -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          7. Disclaimer of Warranties
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">
          THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER
          EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY,
          FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND NON-INFRINGEMENT.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Limitation of Liability -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          8. Limitation of Liability
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">
          IN NO EVENT SHALL FLOJO, INC. BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL,
          CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED TO YOUR USE OF THE SERVICE.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Changes to Terms -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          9. Changes to Terms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">
          We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. We will notify users of
          significant changes by posting a notice on our website. Your continued use of the Service
          after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the modified Terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-4">
          If you have questions about these Terms, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
          <strong>Email:</strong> legal@goflojo.com<br />
          <strong>Website:</strong>
          <a href="https://flojo.io" class="text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 hover:underline"
            >https://flojo.io</a
          >
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</MarketingLayout>
